有，而且其實你不一定要先建 Temp Table。

你的驗證重點只有一句：

來源 CustomerNo 的 HIGHRISK = Migration 後同一個 TS_CUST_ID 底下所有 CustomerNo 的最高 HIGHRISK

直接查出異常即可。

SELECT
    src.CustomerNo AS TS_CUST_ID,
    src.HIGHRISK   AS SRC_HIGHRISK,
    MAX(
        CASE np.HIGHRISK
            WHEN 'H' THEN 3
            WHEN 'M' THEN 2
            WHEN 'L' THEN 1
        END
    ) AS TGT_RISK
FROM BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT src
JOIN BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO sk
    ON src.CustomerNo = sk.TS_CUST_ID
JOIN Customer_Migrate_buffer cm
    ON sk.SK_CUST_ID = cm.CustomerNo
JOIN Cust_NP_Migrate_buffer np
    ON cm.CIF_KEY = np.CIF_KEY
GROUP BY
    src.CustomerNo,
    src.HIGHRISK
HAVING
    CASE src.HIGHRISK
        WHEN 'H' THEN 3
        WHEN 'M' THEN 2
        WHEN 'L' THEN 1
    END
    <>
    MAX(
        CASE np.HIGHRISK
            WHEN 'H' THEN 3
            WHEN 'M' THEN 2
            WHEN 'L' THEN 1
        END
    );

